00:46:06.120 --> 00:46:07.770 align:middle line:90%
for the experiencers.

00:46:07.770 --> 00:46:12.300 align:middle line:84%
And these experiences
occur when the individual

00:46:12.300 --> 00:46:17.170 align:middle line:84%
is physiologically or
psychologically close to death.

00:46:17.170 --> 00:46:21.090 align:middle line:84%
And sometimes the
near-death experience

00:46:21.090 --> 00:46:23.700 align:middle line:90%
is induced by a cardiac arrest.

00:46:23.700 --> 00:46:25.860 align:middle line:84%
Then when there's
a cardiac arrest,

00:46:25.860 --> 00:46:30.340 align:middle line:84%
