flow to the brain very rapidly.

00:46:30.340 --> 00:46:32.730 align:middle line:84%
And if you are measuring
the electrical activity

00:46:32.730 --> 00:46:36.810 align:middle line:84%
in the brain, it
vanishes totally, usually

00:46:36.810 --> 00:46:39.120 align:middle line:90%
after 15 to 20 minutes--

00:46:39.120 --> 00:46:40.500 align:middle line:90%
seconds, pardon.

00:46:40.500 --> 00:46:44.400 align:middle line:84%
And in that kind of state, the
individual, the experiencer,

00:46:44.400 --> 00:46:48.630 align:middle line:84%
is considered to be in a
state of clinical death.

00:46:48.630 --> 00:46:51.990 align:middle line:84%
