00:47:09.135 --> 00:47:12.960 align:middle line:84%
have been a number of
studies in the United States,

00:47:12.960 --> 00:47:18.920 align:middle line:84%
United Kingdom, and other
countries reporting over

00:47:18.920 --> 00:47:23.860 align:middle line:84%
150 cases of people who
were clinically dead,

00:47:23.860 --> 00:47:27.900 align:middle line:84%
and yet they were able
to have mental activity.

00:47:27.900 --> 00:47:30.990 align:middle line:84%
And not only that, but
their mental activity

00:47:30.990 --> 00:47:36.810 align:middle line:84%
was enhanced compared to the
normal state of consciousness.

00:47:36.810 --> 00:47:40.245 align:middle line:84%
